subproject.corporate outcome: Capacities of national and local institutions enhanced to scale up proven MDG acceleration interventions and to plan, monitor, report and evaluate the MDG progress in the context of related national development priorities
subproject.description:
Enhanced Economic Growth is aiming to deliver on four major factors
1- Macro-framework for economic growth corridors developed
2- Enhanced knowledge of federal and regional institutions to facilitate design, leadership and management of EGCs
3- Appropriate EGCs identified and selected for further detailed studies 
4- Various investment plans/projects prepared and ready for implementation
subproject.title: Enhanced Economic Growth
